In the Array Game assignment you have had to review and revisit concepts you may
have forgotten about. These will all be tested on the final exam!
What is an array?
An array is a container of objects that holds values of the same type

How does one make a simple array of Strings?
String[] pizza = new String[20]; 

What is the syntax for a 2-D array?
int[][] array = new int[number1][number2];

What is the syntax for a 3-D array?
int[][][] array = new int[number1][number2][number3];

How does one change the value for the third value in a one dimensional array?
[Give specific code]
String[] pizza = new String[20];
pizza[2] = "peperoni";

What is the syntax for a while loop?
bollean running = true;
While(running){
}

Why use while loops in your game?
to contatly cycle through code without having to copy it

