}

Why was it recommended that you use .toLowerCase() with your Scanner input?
so that it can track both lower and upper case letters for more variety check

You should use different methods when moving the protagonist and to check for
intersections. How? Why?
so that the code for the players movement doesnt get broken because of the enemy
movement; better organization

